<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ⅰ. 부문별 지역경제동향 - 국내 인구이동 ({% if report_info.year is defined and report_info.year %}{{ report_info.year }}{% else %}[연도 입력 필요]{% endif %}년 {% if report_info.quarter is defined and report_info.quarter %}{{ report_info.quarter }}{% else %}[분기 입력 필요]{% endif %}/4분기)</title>
    
    {# 결측치 플레이스홀더 매크로 #}
    {% macro val(value, format="%.1f", suffix="") %}
        {%- if value is none or value == '' or value == '-' or value == 'N/A' -%}
            <span class="editable-placeholder" contenteditable="true">[  ]</span>{{ suffix }}
        {%- else -%}
            {{ format|format(value) }}{{ suffix }}
        {%- endif -%}
    {% endmacro %}
    
    <style>
        /* 기본 리셋 */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: "Malgun Gothic", serif;
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #000;
            background: #fff;
        }
        
        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            padding: 15mm 20mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
        }
        
        @media screen {
            .page {
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
        }
        
        /* 숫자 제목 */
        .section-title {
            font-family: "Malgun Gothic", serif;
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        /* 요약 박스 */
        .summary-box {
            border: 1px dotted #555;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            background-color: transparent;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .summary-box .headline {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            text-indent: -12px;
            padding-left: 12px;
        }
        
        .summary-box .nationwide {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            padding-left: 16px;
            text-indent: -16px;
        }
        
        .summary-box .regional {
            padding-left: 16px;
            text-indent: -16px;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .increase, .decrease {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        /* 상세 박스 */
        .detail-box {
            border: 1px dotted #555;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-box .title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        
        .detail-box .item {
            margin-bottom: 1px;
            line-height: 1.45;
            padding-left: 8px;
            text-indent: -8px;
        }
        
        .detail-box .separator {
            border-top: 1px dotted #888;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        /* 테이블 */
        .table-container {
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        
        .table-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-family: "Malgun Gothic", serif;
        }
        
        .data-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 11pt;
            table-layout: fixed;
        }
        
        .data-table th,
        .data-table td {
            
            padding: 2px 3px;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
            height: 22px;
            word-break: break-word;
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
        }
        
        /* 테이블 헤더 - 연보라색 */
        .data-table th {
            background-color: #e6e0ec;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        
        /* 지역 그룹 셀 */
        .data-table .region-group {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-weight: normal;
            width: 28px;
        }
        
        .data-table .region-name {
            width: 32px;
        }
        
        /* 금액/연령 섹션 */
        .data-table td.amount-section {
            background-color: #fef9e7;
        }
        
        .data-table th.amount-section {
            background-color: #e6e0ec;
        }
        
        .footnote {
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        
        
        /* 결측치 플레이스홀더 */
        .editable-placeholder {
            background-color: #fff59d;
            padding: 0 4px;
            border: 1px dashed #fbc02d;
            color: #5d4037;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .missing-cell {
            background-color: #fff9c4 !important;
        }
        
        sup {
            font-size: 70%;
            vertical-align: super;
        }
        
        @media print {
            .page {
                width: 100%;
                min-height: auto;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .data-table th {
                background-color: #e6e0ec !important;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
                print-color-adjust: exact;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="section-title">{{ report_info.main_section_number | default(7) }}. {{ report_info.main_section_title | default("국내 인구이동") }}</div>
        
        <!-- 요약 박스 -->
        <div class="summary-box">
            <div class="headline">◆ {{ summary_box.headline | default("인구이동은 경기(전입초과), 인천(전입초과) 등 5개 시도에서 전입초과 발생") }}</div>
            <div class="nationwide">□ {{ summary_box.inflow_summary | default("경기(12.7천명), 인천(4.2천명) 등은 20~29세 인구 중심으로 타 시도에서 전입인구 유입") }}</div>
            <div class="regional">○ {{ summary_box.outflow_summary | default("서울(△18.3천명), 대전(△2.8천명) 등은 20~29세 인구 중심으로 타 시도로 전출인구 유출") }}</div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 유입 지역 상세 -->
        <div class="detail-box">
            <div class="title">&lt; 주요 유입지역 및 연령별 유입인구 &gt;</div>
            {% for region in top3_inflow_regions %}
            <div class="item">·{{ region.name }}({{ "{:,.0f}".format(region.net_migration) if region.net_migration is not none else "[  ]" }}명): 
                {% for age in region.ages %}{{ age.name }}({{ "{:,.0f}".format(age.value) if age.value is not none else "[  ]" }}명){% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
            
            <div class="separator"></div>
            
            <!-- 유출 지역 상세 -->
            <div class="title">&lt; 주요 유출지역 및 연령별 유출인구 &gt;</div>
            {% for region in top3_outflow_regions %}
            <div class="item">·{{ region.name }}({{ "{:,.0f}".format(region.net_migration) if region.net_migration is not none else "[  ]" }}명): 
                {% for age in region.ages %}{{ age.name }}({{ "{:,.0f}".format(age.value) if age.value is not none else "[  ]" }}명){% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        
        <!-- 데이터 테이블 -->
        <div class="table-container">
            <div class="table-title">《 국내 인구 순이동<sup>1)</sup> 》</div>
            <table style="border-collapse: collapse !important; border: 1px solid black !important;" class="data-table">
                <thead style="border: 1px solid black !important;">
                    <tr>
                        <th rowspan="2" colspan="2" style="width: 60px;; border: 1px solid black !important"></th>
                        <th colspan="4" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">순이동(천명)</th>
                        <th colspan="2" class="amount-section" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">{{ summary_table.columns.current_quarter | default("2025.2/4") }}</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="width: 58px;; border: 1px solid black !important">{{ summary_table.columns.quarter_columns[0] | default("2023.2/4") }}</th>
                        <th style="width: 58px;; border: 1px solid black !important">{{ summary_table.columns.quarter_columns[1] | default("2024.2/4") }}</th>
                        <th style="width: 58px;; border: 1px solid black !important">{{ summary_table.columns.quarter_columns[2] | default("2025.1/4") }}</th>
                        <th style="width: 58px;; border: 1px solid black !important">{{ summary_table.columns.quarter_columns[3] | default("2025.2/4") }}</th>
                        <th class="amount-section" style="width: 70px;; border: 1px solid black !important">20~29세</th>
                        <th class="amount-section" style="width: 70px;; border: 1px solid black !important">그 외<sup>2)</sup></th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for row in summary_table.rows %}
                    <tr>
                        {% if row.region_group %}
                        <td class="region-group" rowspan="{{ row.rowspan | default(1) }}" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">{{ row.region_group }}</td>
                        <td class="region-name" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">{{ row.sido }}</td>
                        {% elif '전' in row.sido and '국' in row.sido %}
                        <td colspan="2" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">{{ row.sido }}</td>
                        {% else %}
                        <td class="region-name" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">{{ row.sido }}</td>
                        {% endif %}
                        {% for value in row.net_migrations %}
                        <td class="{% if value is none or value == '' or value == '-' %}missing-cell{% endif %}" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">
                            {{ val(value) }}
                        </td>
                        {% endfor %}
                        <td class="amount-section {% if row.age_20_29 is none or row.age_20_29 == '' or row.age_20_29 == '-' %}missing-cell{% endif %}" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">
                            {{ val(row.age_20_29) }}
                        </td>
                        <td class="amount-section {% if row.age_other is none or row.age_other == '' or row.age_other == '-' %}missing-cell{% endif %}" style="border: 1px solid black !important;">
                            {{ val(row.age_other) }}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            
            <div class="footnote">1) 순이동 = 전입자 수 - 전출자 수 (전국 순이동 = 0)</div>
            <div class="footnote">2) 그 외: 0~19세 및 30세 이상 연령층</div>
            <div class="footnote">자료: 국가데이터처</div>
            <div class="footnote">담당: 경제동향통계심의관 지역경제동향과 (042-481-xxxx)</div>
        </div>
        
</body>
</html>
